ai_summary.en: The broader crypto market is entrenched in "Extreme Fear," as indicated by BTC's Fear & Greed Index at 16. Institutional whales on Ethereum, despite a neutral-to-slightly bullish sentiment (0.02), are exhibiting high caution with substantial stablecoin outflows, signaling de-risking. Meanwhile, Solana's more speculative retail segment displays a slightly bearish sentiment (-0.11) but paradoxically shows minor stablecoin inflows, hinting at opportunistic dip-buying with low conviction. This stark divergence amidst macro fear suggests continued market uncertainty and potential consolidation ahead.
ai_summary.zh: 加密市场正处于“极度恐惧”之中，比特币的恐慌与贪婪指数为16。尽管情绪指数微弱偏多（0.02），但以太坊上的机构巨鲸正通过大规模稳定币流出积极去风险化，显示出高度谨慎。与此同时，Solana上更具投机性的散户群体则表现出轻微看跌情绪（-0.11），却出现小额稳定币流入，暗示逢低吸纳的投机行为但信心不足。宏观恐慌下的这种明显分歧预示着短期市场将继续保持不确定性和盘整态势。
